      "code": "PX992010",
      "abbreviation": "PX992010",
      "description": "A self-administered questionnaire to better describe and understand the patient experience and recovery of those with confirmed or suspected COVID-19, with a specific emphasis on Long COVID experience especially with cough, shortness of breath and tightness in chest.",
